main event: A report on unidentified flying objects (UFOs) analyzed by Project Blue Book with references to sightings in Mexico.
interesting points: Analysis by Major Hector Quintanilla identified multiple reflections in a UFO slide,The report details sightings of three UFOs near Guadalajara, Mexico,The objects were captured in slides by witnesses who were in a remote area,The analysis noted that low contrast could have been due to light rays or lens flare,No identifiable signature could be determined from the images viewed under microscopes.
witness description: A son-in-law and daughter traveling in Mexico, described as not previously interested in UFOs.
